      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>37</ID>
      <DefaultText>Tendrils of force caress your mind, almost possessive in their gentleness. A welcome, perhaps, recognition of a kindred spirit.

{ADAM: I have changed the ordering of the Tide nodes here to reflect what the Bloom probably cares about - cmm}</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
